The paper deals with the problem of flip distance between two triangulations, which is a fundamental problem in computational geometry. This problem is closely related to computational geometry and combinatorics, which are covered by the sub-categories cs.CG, cs.DS, cs.DM, cs.CC, and cs.GT. Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
